(263, 75, 'service_content', 'To reduce waste and protect our environment, we offer an Eco-Friendly moving supplies. If you want to buy your moving supplies in advance, you can do so here or call us and well take care of it for you. If your stressing because you need some more supplies don’t worry, the day of your move you can also buy supplies as all of our moving trucks will fully stocked with any supplies you need to make sure your move goes as stress free as possible.'),
