(272, 76, '_service_name', 'field_58748d066c64b'),
(273, 76, 'service_content', 'Life can be hectic, moving shouldn’t have to be. From packing to unpacking, choose us to take care of you every step of the way\r\n<h3>A white glove moving service</h3>\r\nOur white glove movers offer a custom packing service tailored to your needs. Built specifically for you, we take extra care to make sure all items are loaded, unloaded and delivered without any damage. Our team of packing and moving experts can safely wrap and pad any item big or small and properly prepare it for moving.  We take extra steps to make sure to protect your priceless items are moved safely and efficiently. Our white glove movers are experienced and ready to handle specialty items that require additional crating including building custom crates.\r\n\r\n'),
