(1333, 224, 'service_content', '<h3>A home away from your home.</h3>\r\nWe understand that not all moves can happen when you want to. You may need to move before your new home is ready. Often, you have more furniture than you need. No matter what you store or when you need to store it, Austin Moving Forward’s storage facilities take advantage of 24-hour video surveillance and the latest technology to provide a peace of mind, night and day. We go the extra mile and specially handle valuables like art, antiques, books and documents so they will last in storage.\r\n<h3>Delivered when you need it.</h3>\r\nWhen you are ready for your possessions to be delivered from our storage facility, simply call our office and we will set up a speedy delivery. Our professional movers will unload all items in your home or office and take back any gently used boxes. We will also take any recyclable materials from you so that you are not burdened with extra clutter in your new place! We want your experience with us to have as little effect on your day-to-day life.'),
