(5, 1, '2017-01-09 05:04:25', '2017-01-09 05:04:25', 'Your top choice for Moving Companies Austin TX, we are a full service moving company meaning we come out and handle all the moving for you and offer storage services as well. We are a full service Austin Moving company and we can also store your furnishings in our state-of-the-art storage facility, for as long as you need us to. We are licensed, bonded, and fully insured and our services are handled by our trained and experienced Austin Movers, to ensure a hassle free moving process. Our team of professional movers, will disassemble and reassemble your larger furniture, pack and unpack, and protect and wrap your fragile items for transport to your new apartment, home, or office. When choosing us as your Moving Company in Austin you get a month free storage, and a worry-free moving process whether it be for local moving, commercial moving, or statewide moving, we got you covered.\r\nWe’re your best choice when needing a Moving Company Austin TX\r\nOur founder is a busy mother of two who felt it was important that children and future generations grow up in a less toxic world. This is our company’s core belief. Therefore we use recycled boxes wrapping paper and plastic, biodegradable packing adhesives and loaner boxes to reduce our carbon footprint.\r\nTake a look around, view our customer testimonials on our Austin Movers, print yourself a coupon to show our Austin Movers and get started with your FREE quote today. We look forward to helping you along your journey across Austin or across the great state of Texas.', 'About Austin Moving Forward', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2017-02-06 06:19:14', '2017-02-06 06:19:14', '', 0, 'http://amf.dev/?page_id=5', 0, 'page', '', 0),
