(758, 2, '2015-07-22 21:15:45', '2015-07-22 21:15:45', '<a href="http://www.austinmovingforward.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/amf_buildings_1250.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-759 size-medium alignright" src="http://www.austinmovingforward.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/amf_buildings_1250-300x209.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="209" /></a>\n\nSuccessful commercial moves and business office moves require a trusted mover. You want professional service to make a smooth transition that keeps your business moving forward. Every business depends on its customers, financial data, and even trade secrets to be successful. Is the moving company you have chosen to work with the right company?\n<strong>Secure &amp; Confidential</strong>\n\nFirst pick a bonded, insured company with years of moving experience. The moving company should have employees who can handle your secure boxes and other sensitive information and move them with proper handling. Your company’s customer lists, financial information, and trade secrets should be kept secure while moving from an existing space to a new location.\n<strong>Safe &amp; Trusted</strong>\n\nWe recommend working with a moving team that can manage all the details and all the logistics of your move. Your documents, equipment, and data are safe. Austin Moving Forward provides our clients with a secure storage facility, if needed, they can trust that whether storing a single box or a large equipment, it will be inventoried and secured.\n\n<strong>Eco-Friendly</strong>\n\nAcross Texas, everyone is trying to reduce their carbon footprint. At Austin Moving Forward, we buy back all gently used boxes to be re-used and collect all recyclables so that you have less clutter once moved in. Our box re-use program is just one way Austin Moving Forward is continually trying to reduce our carbon footprint and yours.\nIt is important to consider all these things when choosing a commercial moving company for business moves. Trust Austin Moving Forward, Austi