(794, 2, '2015-08-07 16:49:16', '2015-08-07 16:49:16', '<a href="http://www.austinmovingforward.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Dollarphotoclub_211968.jpg"><img class="alignright wp-image-795 size-medium" src="http://www.austinmovingforward.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/Dollarphotoclub_211968-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="200" /></a>\n\n<strong>Moving in Texas? Everything is Better with Austin Moving Forward</strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nPlanning a move in Texas?  Everything is better with Austin Moving Forward, your eco-friendly choice for moving in Texas.\n\n<strong>Moving in the greater Austin area?</strong>\n\nWhether you are moving to/from a dorm or a high rise, your family is expanding, or you’ve hit a milestone of success, Austin Moving Forward has you covered.  It all starts with our free, on-site estimate so you have a reliable quote you can depend on.\n\n<strong>Relocating to Austin?</strong>\n\nAustin is the #1 place to live on many lists, and Austin Moving Forward is Austin’s premiere eco-friendly moving and storage company.  Whether you are relocating from Dallas, Houston, San Antonio, or somewhere along the I35 corridor, trust Austin Moving Forward to give you a reliable quote and a less stressful move.  Let our relocation specialists smooth the way!\n\n<strong>Moving Away from the Music Capital of the World?</strong>\n\nMoving can be stressful, but Austin Moving Forward’s professional relocation specialists help provide peace of mind as you relocate within the Lone Star State.  We can coordinate all aspects of your move so you have the kind of stress-free move you always dreamed of.  Get the job done right with Austin Moving Forward!\n\nCall Austin Moving Forward today!', 'Texas Moves Better', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'texas-moves-better', '', '', '2015-08-07 16:49:16', '2015-08-07 16:49:16', '', 0, 'http://www.austinmovingforward.com/?p=794', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(797, 2, '2015-08-12 21:37:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'You''ve just found out you are moving, but you might be wondering what kind of options you have. There are many moving options, from DIY moves where a moving company moves the belongings you have packed to our concierge service where we pack, crate, move, and unpack or uncrate each and every item.\n\nIn a typical DIY service, you purchase the supplies you need for packing such as boxes, tape, and bubble wrap. You pack it all, the movers move it all and unload the truck at your new residence.\n\nFor professional concierge service moves, the moving company walks you through every step for your move. All the details are coordinated with you so that you have the most flexibility. Your possessions are carefully packed and/or crated, from your clothing to your fine china, and even jet skis when necessary. Upon arrival to your new residence, your belongings are inspected and unpacked and pictures, mirrors, and artwork rehung.\n\nHow do I know if an item should be packed or crated? When an item is crated, it is sometimes an unusual shape or size, or it could be difficult to move statuary due to its composition or fragility. We custom build all crates to fit your valuables using wood materials for the crate and skids and a variety of packing materials inside to safely transport each item individually. Packing involves more traditional packing methods including blankets, boxes repurposed for the job at hand, bubble wrap, and taping.\n\nWhether a do-it-yourself type move is more your style or you prefer the full service concierge route, your ultimate goal is to have all your belongings moved to your new location with no hassle. Contact us at Austin Moving Forward to learn more about all the moving services we offer.', 'DIY Move vs. Hiring Professional Movers?', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', '', '', '', '2015-08-12 21:37:35', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://www.austinmovingforward.com/?p=797', 0, 'post', '', 0),
